<para style="q1">

<verse number="6" style="v" />He says in his heart," I will never fail;</para>

<para style="q1">throughout all generations I will not meet adversity."</para>

<para style="q1">

<verse number="7" style="v" />His mouth is full of cursing and deceptive, harmful words;</para>

<para style="q1">his tongue injures and destroys.</para>
